<dl id="n41017f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41017f">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41017f"> 17(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> calf lows</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The Golden Calf is alluded to in many Koranic passages, <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> R. Jehuda (followed by Geiger) says upon the text (Exod. xxxii. 24), &ldquo;The <mark>calf came forth lowing</mark> and the Israelites beheld it;&rdquo; <small> Richard F. Burton, trans. <a name="RBTE3" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#RBTE3"><cite title="source">Supplemental Nights to the Book of the Thousand Nights and a Night</cite></a> (n.d.) VII, 160n7</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
